00:19:36,430 --> 00:19:40,558
Phesmatos exaud mi,
conjug spiritis et corpe.

416
00:19:40,559 --> 00:19:42,343
Phesmatos exaud mi,

417
00:19:42,344 --> 00:19:44,961
conjug spiritis et corpe.

